  *Explanations:*  
  *P - pull off*  
  *H - hammer on*  
  *B - bend*  
  *R - release bend*  
  */ - slide up*  
  *\ - slide down*  
  *^ - upstroke (the pick moves towards the sky. "Pull")*  
  *v - downstroke (the pick moves towards the ground. "Push")*  
  *(5) - let ring the indicated note, but don't pick*  
